{"tid":1161982,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我同你講 貿易戰係習近平捉緊嘅一盤大棋","createTime":"2019-05-19T14:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T15:13:45.000Z","uid":233118,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"901edc9b332a7f804334af2b3a1fde298772e8fd","tid":1161982,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"近排有好多兒登仔喺度話 中美貿易戰 中國輸硬收硬皮 又話習近平無撚用<br />\n我睇完不知幾想笑 話你戇鳩 怕你嬲<br />\n可能睇到呢度嘅就會話我<del>五</del>三毛<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係我同你講 其實貿易戰係習近平捉嘅一盤大棋 其實你哋全部都誤會曬小熊維尼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可能會話：蝗國而家畀美國收緊皮&nbsp; 習維尼點會係贏家？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺探討呢個問題之前 你哋諗下 世界上最大嘅毒瘤係咩？冇錯 就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國共產黨 同埋佢旗下嘅蝗國人</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個濕鳩黨派一直搜刮國內外民脂民膏 啲人又聲大夾惡 人人得而誅之 但係礙於佢係龐然大物 又卑鄙無恥 一直冇辦法畀外國勢力打敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 簡直就好似打機啲邪惡組織同啲靚咁樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁喺呢個最黑暗嘅時候 我哋就需要一個真正嘅英雄 如果我冇估錯 個嗰人就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雜種習維尼</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢臥薪嘗膽 打爆薄熙來 登上黨主席 推行一帶一路呢啲一聽就會畀人圍插 嘅措施 又用咗大量國家嘅財產嚟打一場唔會勝利嘅戰爭 目的係咩？ 就係要<span style=\"color: red;\">毀滅共產黨嘅根基</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一來佢一嘢洗撚曬咁多年嚟偷呃拐騙嘅錢 等佢嚴重內耗 啲自私自利又短視嘅黨員自然會分黨結派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去搶更大嘅利益 到時分而治之 再逐個擊破 就可以將原本傷天害理嘅黨員徹底消滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同一時間 貿易戰 打到個個中國人破產<br />\n人民被迫食草 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自然人口大幅削減 再次摧毀共產黨嘅根基 再加上維尼用暴政打壓佢地 令人民意識到 共產黨嘅真面目 製造反對聲音 用共產黨最自豪嘅宣傳戰打返自己 以人之道還治其人之身 呢個就係八奇嘅思考領域<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我會知道呢啲嘢？ 大家可以睇下侵侵嘅留言：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REPYtHo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREPYtHo.png&h=e24f1e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n侵侵一面屌柒中國 但係又話習維尼一直係佢朋友 咁即係暗示咗啲乜嘢？<br />\n就係其實佢一直知道習維尼係同佢同一陣線 大家都想中國共產黨收皮 拯救世界&nbsp;但係礙於good cop bad cop 嘅理論 維尼只可以犧牲自己做醜人 捨生取義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再加上近日嗰封beautiful letter 我有理由相信&nbsp; 嗰封其實係遺書道別信 因為習維尼相信 自己已經就快去到盡頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要畀人拉落台批鬥斬頭 於是託付侵侵幫佢做好身後事 如果唔係都解釋唔到點解侵侵之後會咁嬲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你哋可能會話 習近平呢啲冇讀書嘅廢j 點會有咁大抱負 你咁講就大錯特錯 當年佢喺文革受到老毛嘅循循善誘 習得毛主席嘅真傳：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">內鬥</span></span></span> 難能可貴嘅係 佢更加付諸實行 為咗世界而戰 簡直唔可以唔對住佢打飛機致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同一時間 為咗補償台灣長年畀共產黨打壓 雜種就搵咗一個代表去幫助而家頹垣敗瓦嘅台灣發展 冇錯 嗰個人就係高雄市長<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">韓國瑜</span></span> <br />\n你以為佢講嘅高雄迪士尼係假嘅？咁係你哋諗都一啲唔夠深遠 你諗下貿易戰中國收皮 會有幾多囡囡冇飯開 到時一野收曬落高雄 重振當年東莞嘅風采 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外匯收入upupup<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> GDP gogogo <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />台灣仲唔發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜同你班友講都嘥氣 佢唯有大智若愚 扮曬傻仔 當台灣發大財嘅嗰一刻 你哋就會明白佢係幾撚有智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總而言之 當你哋以為trump 先係世界嘅大英雄嘅時候 <span style=\"color: red;\">維尼熊其實先喺背後默默咁樣拯救緊呢個世界</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df467e9b405444c718cae4b6f6b18389ff54a121","tid":1161982,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e4d11f0233efde08591d2e7d80f082134fce13","tid":1161982,"uid":233118,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主分析獨到見解精闢 大家快啲帶住蜜糖參拜習維尼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：維尼罪大滔天 搞到百姓怨聲載道"},{"pid":"40d0485f9f1e5c9c862af2eec73e2dd74e35a7da","tid":1161982,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"有無講稿分享下"},{"pid":"02f709d2518eb769218d222086e07af29d9ab648","tid":1161982,"uid":93062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:41:14.000Z","msg":"有病睇醫生食藥"},{"pid":"2b516127364cce32f83b5140f06686e0e8af5d58","tid":1161982,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"反逆的習習總"},{"pid":"9aac1976f6afee34d5ac4346543f6aecd101fffd","tid":1161982,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"收到風有個古代日本棋士既靈魂教雜總捉棋"},{"pid":"0ee61fa14cf5bb0292453fa0cb6a7cae00d03102","tid":1161982,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:46:40.000Z","msg":"維尼幾時做過黨主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做假膠鳩吹都熟悉下D基本事實先啦"},{"pid":"2fcb0033866257c787b5ce6876f1e3a6ae0edccc","tid":1161982,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee61fa14cf5bb0292453fa0cb6a7cae00d03102","tid":1161982,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:46:40.000Z","msg":"維尼幾時做過黨主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做假膠鳩吹都熟悉下D基本事實先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:48:35.000Z","msg":"維尼唔識字 唔可以做書記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a5ba1451f87837b1d4f8761a0256b39ee70a49","tid":1161982,"uid":45178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"夾埋沽空股市搵錢嘅朋友就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9832ab1205c103fabd066165b04a43dcb9ba944","tid":1161982,"uid":12015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:55:32.000Z","msg":"一個月大限而定<br />\n但哩幾日兩邊都無乜聲氣<br />\n大師分析下係咪暴風雨前夕"},{"pid":"579244e3e1dac9fface4ee39a496ebb7232f1fbd","tid":1161982,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9832ab1205c103fabd066165b04a43dcb9ba944","tid":1161982,"uid":12015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:55:32.000Z","msg":"一個月大限而定<br />\n但哩幾日兩邊都無乜聲氣<br />\n大師分析下係咪暴風雨前夕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"美國急住封殺華為<br />\n一定係華為擁有不可告人嘅秘密<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再加上之前5毛降價<br />\n如果我冇估錯<br />\n華為一定掌握咗植入人體嘅晶片技術<br />\n所以可以生產大量嘅5毛 <br />\n再使用5g技術大規模控制網絡水軍<br />\n令到供應量上升 價格下跌<br />\n近排都冇聲出 一定係雙方都積極準備喺網上應戰 項時將會係google 大戰千萬水軍大腦 <br />\n科網股爆炸 電腦大爆炸"},{"pid":"a7c892dfa86ce0183d60a5513e6bfa2ad7a8fdca","tid":1161982,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:13:45.000Z","msg":"本來都講得幾好，但最尾台灣個part , 膠味太濃，破壞曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}